title: Impeachment, Sen. Tina Smith, Rep. Comer
itunes:title: Impeachment, Sen. Tina Smith, Rep. Comer
description:
Guests: Jeanne Sheehan Zaino, Bloomberg politics contributor, and Iona College Professor, Adam Goodman, Republican media strategist, columnist and partner at Ballard Partners in Washington, Senator Tina Smith of Minnesota and Rep. James Comer, a Republican representing Kentucky's 1st district.
